billion US dollars into 300 companies in Tianjin, northern China's
largest coastal city.
</P>
<P>
Many of the multinationals, which are from 32 countries and
regions, have invested in the Tianjin Development Zone, and 25 out
of the world's top 100 companies are involved in the city's
development, with six projects each having at least 100 million US
dollars in investment.
</P>
