equipment, the electronics, bio-engineering, machinery, and
foodstuff sectors have been improving.
</P>
<P>
State-owned enterprises are getting help by providing parts and
accessories for overseas-funded companies, and some enterprises
funded by big-name companies like the US's Motorola and Samsung of
the Republic of Korea have increased their localization rate to
more than 50 percent. 
