down from 1.8543 on Thursday; 1.6595 British pounds, down from
1.6633; 6.1919 French francs, down from 6.2120; 1.5243 Swiss
francs, down from 1.5330; 1,821 Italian lire, down from 1,828 and
1.4194 Canadian dollars, down from 1.4198. 
