third straight session.
</P>
<P>
The S&AMP;P's 500 stock list was up 0.95 to 1,120.96 and the NYSE
composite index rose 1.04 to 583.08. The technology heavy Nasdaq
composite index was up 2.11 to 1,855.08 and the American Stock
Exchange composite index rose 0.16 to 746.63. 
